<Left Alt>+<Left Button>  Emulate middle mouse button        @{"1.9.2" LINK PPaintCD:H/7/0/4/0002/Main 530}
<Shift>+<Disk Eject>      Personal Paint screen to front     @{"1.10.4" LINK PPaintCD:H/7/0/4/0002/Main 839}
<Shift>+<Mouse Move>      Constrain mouse movement           @{"3.1.2" LINK PPaintCD:H/7/0/4/0017/Main 87}
